BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Tour of the R42
DTSTART;TZID=Europe/Berlin:20260605T100000
DTEND;TZID=Europe/Berlin:20260605T130000
DESCRIPTION:The R42 ecosystem brings together gaming\, dining\, events\, c
 ontent production\, work\, and living across seven floors. This concept\, 
 unique in Germany\, fosters innovative ideas at the intersection of busine
 ss and gaming throughout the region. Find inspiration here across nearly 2
 \,000 m². R42 combines gaming\, dining\, events\, content production\, an
 d work. (Address: Ritterstr. 42\, 04109 Leipzig)
LOCATION:R42
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Guided tour of the Security Lab
DTSTART;TZID=Europe/Berlin:20260605T103000
DTEND;TZID=Europe/Berlin:20260605T113000
DESCRIPTION:The interactive innovation lab Cyber Security Lab Leipzig (CSL
 ²) is a place where you can experience IT security firsthand. Through han
 ds-on workshops\, demonstrations\, and interactive sessions\, we deliver p
 ractical\, real-world knowledge. Try out one of our innovative workbenches
  here and discover cyber security in a whole new way. The lab is located o
 n the 3rd floor at Goerdelerring 9 in Leipzig. 
LOCATION:Security Lab
END:VEVENT
